@startuml SequencePayment
title TIMELAPSE - Sequência: Ativação Pro (UC003)
actor User
participant DesktopApp
participant ControlPlane
participant AuthAPI
participant LicenseManager
participant EmailService

User -> DesktopApp: Clica "Ativar Pro"
DesktopApp -> User: Solicita código da org
User -> DesktopApp: Informa código
DesktopApp -> User: Solicita email
User -> DesktopApp: Informa email

DesktopApp -> ControlPlane: POST /auth/magic-link {email, orgCode}
ControlPlane -> AuthAPI: Validar orgCode + criar token
AuthAPI -> EmailService: Enviar Magic Link
EmailService -> User: Email recebido
ControlPlane -> DesktopApp: 200 OK

User -> DesktopApp: Clica no link
DesktopApp -> ControlPlane: POST /auth/verify {token}
ControlPlane -> AuthAPI: Validar token
AuthAPI -> ControlPlane: User + Org
ControlPlane -> LicenseManager: Ativar Pro para org
LicenseManager -> LicenseManager: Atualiza licença
LicenseManager -> ControlPlane: Licença ativada
ControlPlane -> DesktopApp: JWT + Pro ativo
DesktopApp -> User: Acesso Pro liberado
@enduml
